name: SNError.Code
desc: The enumerated error codes that the Sound Analysis framework produces.

items.name: case invalidModel
items.desc: An error that indicates the sound classifier’s underlying Core ML model is an invalid model type.

items.name: case invalidFormat
items.desc: An error that indicates the audio data’s format isn’t valid.

items.name: case invalidFile
items.desc: An error that indicates an audio file is invalid.

items.name: case operationFailed
items.desc: An error that occurs when the framework fails to analyze audio.

items.name: case unknownError
items.desc: An error that represents a failure that no other error handles.
